DTSTART:20260310T154500Z
DESCRIPTION:Location Type: Online Event sponsors: UW Bothell General Facult
	y Organization Accessibility Contact: dawn3@uw.edu If you would like to at
	tend\, please email Dawn Moncalieri\, GFO Progr am Coordinator\, at dawn3@
