	 WEEK PRIOR TO MEET ING\\*\\*\\*\n\nThe Executive Council is an elected fa
	culty council of the GFO. Its responsibilities are to advise the Chance ll
	or and Vice Chancellors on matters involving academic policy\, policy rega
