SUMMARY:North End Ecosocialism Reading Group
DTSTAMP:20260307T213104Z
DTSTART:20260312T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Armistice Coffee Roosevelt\\\, to discuss the Prefac
	e and Part I of the book Practical Radicals: Seven Strategies to Change th
	e World\\\, by Deepak Bhargava and Stephanie Luce. \\nYou don’t have to li
	ve in the north end\\\, and you can feel free to join the conversation eve
	n if you haven’t had time to read.  Our biweekly discussions seek to infor
	m strategies for winning a democratic socialist society that thrives ecolo
	gically. All are welcome! \\nWe sit outdoors in a breezeway–dress warm. An
	y questions or difficulty getting the book\\\, please email greennewdeal@s
	eattledsa.org.\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/north-end-ecosocialism-read
	ing-group-4/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
